# INTRAgenic connections
First+:Internal+                           Internal+:Terminal+                        7:2965                 
Internal-:Terminal-                        First-:Internal-                           7:2965                 
First+                                     Intron+                                    1:1                    
Internal+                                  Intron+                                    1:1                    
